short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome extension to navigate to source.roslyn.io from github Roslyn source

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is for Roslyn developers. 
When viewing Roslyn source code on GitHub, select a class name and find it on source.roslyn.io with the "Lookup on Roslyn.io" context menu.
